name: Small Van
description: Ford Transit Connect, Vauxhall Combo or similar. Ideal for 8-12 cardboard removal boxes or one kitchen appliance.

name: Medium Van
description: Ford Transit, Volkswagen Transporter or similar. Ideal for small moves and can generally take one or two people's personal belongings of up to 30 to 40 assorted moving boxes, or a single large item of furniture such as a sofa or bed.

name: Large Van
description: Mercedes Sprinter XLWB or similar.  Ideal for moving one or two people from a flat with a small amount of furniture and white goods, or for several items of furniture alone such as a three seat sofa, double bed, armchair and chest of drawers. Avg loading dimesions 4.3x2.2x1.8m

name: Box/Luton Van
description: A Luton or box van. Ideal for moving a two bedroom flat or small house with up top 40 boxes of personal belongings, dining table and chairs, two and three seat sofas, two double beds, wardrobes, chest of drawers and all kitchen white goods. Avg loading dimesions 3.9x2.2x2m
